import pandas as pd
from prophet import Prophet
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
%matplotlib inline


date_range = pd.date_range(start='2015-01-01', end='2024-12-31', freq='D')
import numpy as np
np.random.seed(42)
gold_prices = 1200 + np.cumsum(np.random.normal(loc=0.05, scale=2, size=len(date_range)))


df = pd.DataFrame({
    'ds': date_range,
    'y': gold_prices
})


model = Prophet(yearly_seasonality=True, weekly_seasonality=True)
model.fit(df)

future = model.make_future_dataframe(periods=365)
forecast = model.predict(future)

model.plot(forecast)
plt.title("Gold Price Forecast (Dummy Data)")
plt.xlabel("Date")
plt.ylabel("Price (USD)")
plt.show()


model.plot_components(forecast)
plt.show()

import pandas as pd
from prophet import Prophet
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
from sklearn.metrics import mean_absolute_error, mean_squared_error


date_range = pd.date_range(start='2015-01-01', end='2024-12-31', freq='D')
np.random.seed(42)
gold_prices = 1200 + np.cumsum(np.random.normal(loc=0.05, scale=2, size=len(date_range)))


df = pd.DataFrame({'ds': date_range, 'y': gold_prices})


holidays = pd.DataFrame({
    'holiday': ['Diwali'] * 9 + ['Christmas'] * 9,  
    'ds': ['2015-11-11', '2016-10-30', '2017-10-19', '2018-11-07', '2019-10-27', '2020-11-14',
           '2021-11-04', '2022-10-24', '2023-11-12',  
           '2015-12-25', '2016-12-25', '2017-12-25', '2018-12-25', '2019-12-25', '2020-12-25',
           '2021-12-25', '2022-12-25', '2023-12-25'],
    'lower_window': 0,
    'upper_window': 1
})

model = Prophet(yearly_seasonality=True, weekly_seasonality=True, holidays=holidays)
model.add_seasonality(name='monthly', period=30.5, fourier_order=5)  
model.fit(df)


future = model.make_future_dataframe(periods=365)
forecast = model.predict(future)


actual = df['y'][-365:].values
predicted = forecast['yhat'][-365:].values

mae = mean_absolute_error(actual, predicted)
rmse = np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(actual, predicted))

print(f"Mean Absolute Error (MAE): {mae:.2f}")
print(f"Root Mean Squared Error (RMSE): {rmse:.2f}")


model.plot(forecast)
plt.title("Gold Price Forecast (Dummy Data) with Seasonality & Holidays")
plt.xlabel("Date")
plt.ylabel("Price (USD)")
plt.show()


model.plot_components(forecast)
plt.show()
